    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 113.</p><p>Critical Edge</p><p>Infusion, Vorpal</p><p>Weapon: Any light weapon Classes: Fighter, Rogue Channeling Time: 1 action Base LP Cost: 1 LP Range: Self Duration: Concentration, up to 1 minute</p><p>You channel lethal nimbleness into your weapon, infusing it with an edge that finds every gap in a creature’s defenses. For the duration, the infused weapon’s critical hit range is increased by 3.</p></div>",
